    "Already was old Titan's concubine whitening upon the Orient's balcony, outside the arms of her sweet paramour; already was her forehead shining bright with gems, arranged according to the shape of that cold beast, which smites one with its tail; and Night had of the steps wherewith she climbs, already taken two where we were then, and now the third was lowering its wings; when I, who had somewhat of Adam in me, o'ercome with sleep, reclined upon the grass, on which all five of us were sitting then.",
