    "He answered: \"When the P's, which still remain almost extinct upon thy brow, are quite erased, as one is now, thy feet will so be conquered by good will, that they will feel not only no fatigue, but it will be a pleasure to them to be upward urged.\"",
    "I then did as do those, who go about with something on their head they know not of, till others' gestures cause them to suspect;",
